messages.message: Looks like my changes broke the login buttons on aihub-sandbox and crafting-cyp :sweat_smile: . For now, you can log in by going to https://crafting-cyp.test.instabase.com/account/login or https://aihub-sandbox.internal.instabase.com/account/login
I was able to reproduce it locally by running server-nginx in production mode. This should fix the issue: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/70681
